                                <li><p>The <m>x -</m>intercept is a horizontal asymptote</p></li>
                                <li><p>The exponential function is 1 – 1. Algebraically if <m>b^{x} = b^{y}</m>, then <m>x = y</m></p></li>
                            </ol>
                          </p>
